asking for permission
to meet The Master of Frost.


8
00:02:50,810 --> 00:02:53,660
I am friends with the Frostwolf tribe


9
00:02:55,170 --> 00:02:57,170
as well as The Master of Frost.


10
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:58,400
Guys,


11
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,690
can't you feel that?


12
00:03:08,050 --> 00:03:09,580
Did your master


13
00:03:10,090 --> 00:03:12,140
want you to stop me


14
00:03:12,890 --> 00:03:14,490
or attack me?


15
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,300
If I take another step further,


16
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:20,020
are you two going to attack?


17
